and infallible method...

75
00:11:05,245 --> 00:11:08,544
...of insuring his obedience.

76
00:11:15,855 --> 00:11:17,220
You're perfect.

77
00:11:18,758 --> 00:11:20,248
I must have you.

78
00:11:24,364 --> 00:11:27,356
What are you talking about?
It's like you don't even care!

79
